EXTRACTED VALUE: With 16 players and 16 guns blazing, the game is violent bliss, and certainly a war demanding to be fought over and over again. [Apr 2006, p.58]
Call of Duty 4's engrossing story, realistic graphics and compelling gameplay makes this shooter one of the releases of the year.
Halo 3 is an excellent first-person shooter, and with it, Bungie ends its trilogy on a strong note.
